SELECT id,AccountId, account.AnnualRevenue,ICP_Profile__c,account.ICP_Profile__c,CurrencyIsoCode,account.CurrencyIsoCode from Opportunity where id IN('006fw000002GoHSAA0', '006fw000009NXDLAA4','006fw0000050uaPAAQ','006fw000003fbzZAAQ')



While configuring dashboard, if data coming incorrect, login from user and check if data actually exists or no because sometimes the report is wrong and they are not the owner, in my case in a quota dashboard data was not coming correctly so check by logging in as user if they are not the owner, they were the sales user and report was running with the filter:
Show Me:
My Quotas
but the owner was abrar ali


Whenever testing dashboard or Report, always login as user and check records opening their reports for better clarity








